Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.01,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.05,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:24.19,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.89,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:33.29,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.10,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.84,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:49.33,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Repaint the time that has been stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:57.05,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:05.99,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.30,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:18.57,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Recover the last piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.41,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, you went to a school in the\nmiddle of the city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:41.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, a hikikomori, actually went to\na place with lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's big progress, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, I'm impressed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I might as well say that my hikikomori\ncondition has been cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you should be fine going\noutside by yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I'm not hikikomori anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx4\fry22\frz256.109\c&HDD9E2E&\3c&H0D0E0A&\4c&H53EDF6&\move(201,109,200,-120,0,3513)}Kokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz12.916\fscx36.25\fscy65\fnAriosto\pos(271,57)\c&HA49E96&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}Introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz12.916\fscx36.25\fscy65\fnAriosto\c&HA49E96&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(280,96)}Development
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz12.916\fscx36.25\fscy65\fnAriosto\c&HA49E96&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(290,133)}Turn in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz12.916\fscx36.25\fscy65\fnAriosto\c&HA49E96&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(294,166)}Conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know the project is due today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup! I got it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx48\fry2\frz309.413\fscx48.75\fscy71.25\c&H181818&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(148,171)}\NCLASS 2-3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx48\fry2\frz309.413\fscx48.75\fscy71.25\c&H181818&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(149,183)}Tatsuhiro Sato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like your work is pretty\namateurish actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! Is it a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eject!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, it was them behind this all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:14.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the victim of a conspiracy plotted by the NHK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St... Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you do this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, you've been paying for my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,People always say that summer colds\ntake a long time to get over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you really have been sick for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like, my body still feels sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At first, I thought your hikikomori\ncondition got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember, I went to your school\nthe other day by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a big liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy plotted by the NHK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ever since I visited Yamazaki's school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my hikikomiri condition has gotten much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't even want to answer my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to even live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But dying is a pain in the ass too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish I could just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what would have happened to me\nif Yamazaki had never come to check on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:29.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just lied to Yamazaki saying\NI had a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he's going to find out\nthat's a lie sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fight, Sato! Fight against the\nenemy's conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! Our common enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-H-K!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must fight against the conspiracy plotted\nby the Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:58.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fight against them?\NBut I don't have any weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You do have weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Love and courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:06.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't have love or courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? This is certainly unusual.\NTelephone's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? This is certainly unusual.\NTelephone's calling you!\NA phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's been some kind of\naccident or something?\NA phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Telephone?\NA phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:35.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx37.5\fscy38.75\org(224,105)\frx18\fry14\frz23.69\pos(225,103)\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7AE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&}RECORDING...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm not available to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you wish to send me a fax,\nplease press your send button now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? It's Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have some business in Tokyo,\nso I'm coming up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was thinking I should drop by\nand see you while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we could discuss your future plans\nand stuff then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(138,128)\frz21.852\fscx58.75\fscy63.75\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7BE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&}RECORDING...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,\NAnd we could discuss your future plans\nand stuff then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom's coming here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Discuss my future plans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she planning to make me move back home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me a freakin' break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After everything I've done to move to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd just be a loser if I move back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro? Oh, you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I answered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:35.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're home, answer the phone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:39.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I just came back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? Then I guess you still haven't\nchecked your message,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but my class reunion is coming up on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Three days from today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it looks like I'll have some free time\nthe day before the reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I want to see you and discuss some things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Two days from today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't just keep on wasting your time doing\nnothing in Tokyo forever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it time for you to come back home\nand get a job down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides you'll never be able to\nget married at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm fine, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I've already found a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a small software company, but I've been\nwriting scripts and stuff for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I haven't told you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but there's someone I'm considering\ngetting married to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, I've pretty much decided on\nsettling down here in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, good for you, Tatsuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But good, you've got a job now\nand you're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, the marriage part isn't gonna\nhappen anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You see, they don't pay you a whole lot\nwhen you start a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all right! Just knowing that you've\ngot a girlfriend is such a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have to let me meet her when\NI come to Tokyo, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll call you again with the\nflight information and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz41.49\frx354\fry24\pos(329,51)\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7BE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&}IN USE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't buy into it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you tell it's a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Software company... script writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, be more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop being so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M... Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err, it's not Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Mr. Tatsuhiro Sato's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, this is the right number then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, I've been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven't shown up for counseling\nor answered your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Misaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One million yen penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, I have a really good reason\nfor this whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First of all, I have a more important\nthing to worry about right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I just found out that my mother\nis coming to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you told her you've got a job\nat a promising company
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and a girlfriend who's going to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are limits to how much\nyou should make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was planning to drag me back home\nunless I told her stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have two more days before she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:42.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to come up with a way to\nfool her before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A company and a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice, do I, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:56.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't mind pretending to be your girlfriend\nfor a day if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there's Yamazaki!\NI don't mind pretending to be your girlfriend\nfor a day if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there's Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just have to ask Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:03.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ya... Yamazaki is going to be your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:09.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't do that! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no time to waste!\NI'm gonna ask Yamazaki right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki! Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A company! We're gonna make\na company, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can establish a company with as\nlittle as one yen capital these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we establish a company, I can fool my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:12:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, we were gonna make the world's preeminent\ngame company to begin with anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just that our plan has been\naccelerated a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're are going to proudly bring our own\nbrand to the game industry, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our brand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sounds great! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\fscx188.75\fscy202.5\b1\pos(195,115)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx166.25\fscy183.75\pos(188,149)}LET'S PICK A COMPANY NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's pick a company name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, let's pick a company name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't we take "Sa" from Sato\nand '"Yama" from Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and call it "Sayama Company"!\NHow's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But then it sounds like a person named\NSayama founded the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what about something non-Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't memorize all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx161.25\fscy175\pos(192,148)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY LOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make a company logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, for now let's say that our\ncompany name is '"Y.S. Company."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not happy with the name either,\nso let's change it once we become big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next up is the company logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since it's '"Y.S.", how about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like a logo on the baseball cap\nfor some baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, for now, just for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx121.25\fscy157.5\pos(191,143)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make a company song!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:18.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Company song! Company song!\NCompany song for Y. S!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx128.75\fscy156.25\pos(190,144)}LET'S MAKE BUSINESS CARDS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make business cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0\fs14\pos(192,132)}President     {\fs25}Kaoru Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(208,201)\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0}Y.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,President, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd love to call myself "co-president,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I've already told my mother\nthat I found a job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got a job title that's perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0\fs14\pos(188,130)}NEET                   {\fs25}Tatsuhiro Sato
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(208,201)\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0}Y.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,NEET?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That explains your current status\nin on simple word, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:45.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm working hard so that she doesn't find out\nthat's what I am, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First of all, NEET isn't a business title!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx125\fscy161.25\pos(189,143)}LET'S MAKE A RECEPTION DESK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make a reception desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The reception desk is the face of the company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:58.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Therefore, we're going to ask her to be\nthe receptionist for our company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\shad0\bord1.5\pos(182,159)\frz37.087\3c&HFFFFFF&}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord1.5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx70\fscy82.5\pos(225,202)\frz300.744}RECEPTION DESK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now our company is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really going to show\nthis to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Basically, at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,what we need is for it to appear as though\nour company is legit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because you don't really want to\nbring her to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0\frz341.774\pos(187,124)}Tatsuhiro Sato
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H6B6C69&\bord0\shad0\fscx65\fscy63.75\frz341.249\pos(187,180)}Y.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro Sato\NY.s. CompanyLimited\NI think she'll be convinced\nif I show this business card to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How are you going to fool her about the\ngirlfriend who's going to marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I forgot about that problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want me to, I can pretend to be\nyour girlfriend for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFF4&\3c&HFFFFBC&\shad0\fscx57.5\fscy67.5\frz27.352\pos(142,87)}Kashiwa Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:54.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure Senpai will help me out on\nthis one if I explain the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, it's possible that something intended\nas a lie could come true too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? Senpai? It's Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I already have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have an appointment with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My only hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this,\NI guess I'll have Yamazaki dress in drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:33.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Mother! I'm Kaoru Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hell no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't be able to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can do it for you, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,play your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:17.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, do we really have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, when you lie, it's written\nall over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we don't have at least one real date beforehand,\nshe'll be able to tell you're lying right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:31.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I go to some place with a bunch of people,\nthe same thing might happen to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we're together, I'm sure you'll be fine.
