Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:03.05,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Honto ni tsutaetai daiji na sain de\NIs actually the real sign that I want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:10.98,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Nanigeni kimi ni shigusa wo misete iru\NI send you signals through casual gestures
