Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\frz337.228\fscx83.75\fscy90\c&H975E4B&\pos(143,202)}Cheese {\c&HC7BFBA&}(cream cheese)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx83.75\fscy90\frz338.787\pos(108,233)\c&H9A604F&}Mont Blanc
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:17.37,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Atarashii betsu no sekai no tobira no arika e\NThey invite you to the place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.96,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Atarashii betsu no sekai no tobira no arika e\NWhere there's a door to a different new world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:30.97,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Tabuu wo yabutta toki no shougeki wa\NThe shock you get from breaking a taboo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:39.55,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Kitto sore de sunao ni narerudeshou\NWill surely make you honest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:44.02,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Daaku saido ni tsuitekite\NCome with me to the dark side
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:48.05,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Omoi no naka ni hoshizora wo egakitai kara\NBecause I want to draw a starry sky inside your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.62,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Kagami no naka ni haitte kite\NCome inside the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.84,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Futari dake de\NJust the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:57.10,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}ltsumademo itsumademo itsumademo itsumademo\NForever, forever, forever, forever
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.01,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFB908C&\bord2.5\an8\c&H3FFCFF&\fs20}Hibikitai heya\NInside the room where we resonate together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess this is what a so-called\N"normal relationship" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should've made it more official and\ndated each other back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna try walking arm in arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We look more like a real couple that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that I'm feeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could this be the sign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she coming on to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this lie turning into a truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this lie turning into a truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next time will be the real deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better clean up your apartment,\nor your mother will be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:15.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we're going to pretend to be a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,won't it be a problem if we don't\nknow more about each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your name is about the only thing\NI know about you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:32.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I know you very well, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Name, Tatsuhiro Sato.\NDate of birth, January 28th, Aquarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blood type A.\NYou were born in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your hobby is watching videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and recently you've gotten into gal games\nand collecting pictures of a "graphic" nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last place you attended school was at\NHeisei Bunka University, a private school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father's name is Tatsuo.\NMother's name is Shizue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you know so much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You told me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have a good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Mr. Tatsuhiro Sato's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why does she knows the\nphone number to my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only people I've given that number to\nare my parents back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven't told me anything\nabout yourself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:33.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be a problem if I don't know anything about you\nwhen my mother asks me, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Absolutely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell you, but you have to memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, I'll tell you about my family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My grandfather is French\nand his name is Goerges Brufelles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My grandmother is a Japanese prima donna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:59.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They met at Port Moresby and fell in love.\NThey came back to Japan and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:04.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then my mother was born and she got married\nto my father, an elite businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:12.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I was born, but now I live with my relatives\ndue to unavoidable familial circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that? You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S... Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what is my grandfather's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,John... Brook... Brooklyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong! It's Georges Brufelles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, you have to remember it by tomorrow.\NThat's your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:34.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Georges Brufelles, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,George BI... No, Bly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:42.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, it's obviously a lie!\NWhat does she mean, he's French?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who is she?
