Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:15.35,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa, ababa, dancing baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:22.80,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.31,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:25.74,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,We were all loved equally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.24,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as it's supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.78,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.11,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:31.88,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Each destiny takes a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.18,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:34.82,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some can look at other's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:36.25,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others can't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.72,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some get to learn love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.19,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.79,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:42.22,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:45.36,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,A baby, a baby human till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:51.33,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Oh, what an adorable baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:54.30,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"I just want to love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.80,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.34,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:23:00.24,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,The baby she is holding is really a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:01.84,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Ababa!" I snicker to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.24,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiding in my pretended innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:04.88,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so easy to be a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.21,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should be one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:07.88,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa! Dance, multiply
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:09.02,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,And take it to space!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:09.78,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:10.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:11.29,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:11.95,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:14.26,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:15.95,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Misaki Nakahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, Y.S. Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe a cute girl like her\nwill be my daughter-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to Chinatown!"
